summary: Master's student of Econometrics and Operations Research with a keen interest in mathematical finance, in particular stochastic calculus. My strong analytical skills and problem-solving abilities have been honed through rigorous academic training. If you're looking for an enthusiastic and diligent team player with a passion for risk management, please feel free to connect with me.
